subject: Soccer
UEFA Champions League (Soccer)
lead_paragraph: Yaya Sanogo ended his 15-month wait to score for Arsenal, helping it beat visiting Borussia Dortmund, 2-0, and qualify for the Champions League knockout phase for the 15th successive season.
